        content: "Tailwind suportă două strategii de dark mode:\n\n```js\n// tailwind.config.js\nmodule.exports = {\n  darkMode: 'class',   // Toggle manual cu clasa .dark pe <html>\n  // sau:\n  darkMode: 'media',   // Urmărește preferința sistemului\n  // sau:\n  darkMode: ['class', '[data-theme=\"dark\"]'], // Custom selector\n};\n```\n\n**Strategia 'class' (recomandată):**\n```js\n// Toggle în JavaScript\ndocument.documentElement.classList.toggle('dark');\n\n// Sau cu data attribute:\ndocument.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'dark');\n```\n\n```html\n<!-- HTML cu dark mode classes -->\n<div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-gray-900 dark:text-white\">\n  <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400\">\n    Titlul paginii\n  </h1>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300\">\n    Conținut text\n  </p>\n  <button class=\"bg-indigo-600 dark:bg-indigo-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded\">\n    Buton\n  </button>\n</div>\n```\n\n**Persistenta preferintei:**\n```js\n// Salvare în localStorage\nconst theme = localStorage.getItem('theme') || \n  (window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches ? 'dark' : 'light');\ndocument.documentElement.classList.toggle('dark', theme === 'dark');\n```"
